  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "SALES & MARKETING MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>The Sales &amp; Marketing Manager will be responsible for driving brand awareness and implementing marketing strategies for SOEASY.SG LLP. This role focuses on promoting household electrical appliances through effective marketing campaigns, digital engagement, and brand management initiatives.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>SPECIFIC RESPONSIBILITIES:  </p>\n<p>1. Develop and execute marketing strategies</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>2. Manage digital marketing activities (website, social media, online campaigns)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>3. Design and coordinate marketing materials (brochures, catalogues, presentations)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>4. Plan and coordinate promotional events and product showcases</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>5. Conduct market and industry research to identify trends</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>6. Prepare newsletters, press releases, and communications</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>TECHNICAL SKILLS AND COMPETENCIES:</p>\n<p>1. Ability to design structured marketing plans and apply strategic thinking to align them with business goals and market trends.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>2. Proficiency in digital marketing platforms while applying creativity to design and execute effective online campaigns.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>3. Ability to create marketing collaterals using design tools while ensuring accuracy, consistency, and attention to detail.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>4. Capability to plan events by coordinating logistics and vendors while applying strong organizational skills.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>5. Skill in gathering and analyzing market data while applying analytical thinking to produce actionable insights.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>6. Ability to write professional business communications that are clear, engaging, and suitable for diverse audiences. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>ATTACHMENT: 6 MONTHS</p>",
